			<p>You can find more about me in the <a href="/about">about</a> part of the website.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="flow">
			<h2>links</h2>
			<div class="block-div">
				<p>You can find me in these places:</p>
				<a href="https://github.com/12beesinatrenchcoat">12beesinatrenchcoat</a>
				<a href="https://twitter.com/12bz_trenchcoat">@12bz_trenchcoat</a>
				<a href="https://www.youtube.com/c/AndyChanPineapples">andy chan</a>
